v1.0.7 - admin abuse fixes

Changes:
+ If you cannot afford a box, you can continue unboxxing and it'll just wait to unbox another until you can afford it
+ Changed Ivory Solarizer model, to fix bad collisions with ore
+ Fixed Z-Fighting inside of Moonstone Dropper
+ Removed Corium Dropper from #crazy-unboxes Discord channel, due to being a common Secret item
+ Advanced Tooltips setting now hides potion durations when toggled on
+ New icons for the Ivory Solarizer and shiny versions of the Dyson Module
+ Added 'Oil Well' description about how fire interacts with the upgrader

Bug Fixes:
+ Fixed a floating point error inside of Advanced Tooltips
+ Fixed 'The Parent property of OreTemplate is locked, current parent: NULL, new parent Debris' error
+ Removed floating items in the distance
+ Ore is now cleared from your base when you load a layout, clear your base, or buy a plot upgrade
+ You no longer unbox immediately on join if you stop unboxxing and then rejoin
+ Fixed a bug that flagged you couldn't afford a crate you actually could afford
